text: Sangvi is a village in Parola Taluka of Jalgaon district in northwestern part of the state of Maharashtra, India. ==Geography== Sangvi is located at .Falling Rain Genomics, Inc - Sangvi It has an average elevation of 197 metres (649 feet).
